<h2 id="multcomp-and-nlwaldtest-joint-coefficient-tests" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#multcomp-and-nlwaldtest-joint-coefficient-tests" aria-hidden="true">#</a> multcomp and nlWaldTest: Joint coefficient tests</h2>
